00:39:04,740 --> 00:39:05,720
I'm sorry.

548
00:39:07,070 --> 00:39:08,170
I'm sorry.

549
00:39:09,410 --> 00:39:11,310
I kept trying to call you just now.

550
00:39:13,300 --> 00:39:14,600
But you didn't answer.

551
00:39:16,610 --> 00:39:18,550
I thought something had happened to you.

552
00:39:19,350 --> 00:39:20,370
No such thing.

553
00:39:20,670 --> 00:39:22,300
I don't have my phone on me, that's all.

554
00:39:32,190 --> 00:39:35,210
Right now, in my life,
aside from Xiao Jun,

555
00:39:35,780 --> 00:39:38,360
there's nothing else
that is worth mentioning.

556
00:39:39,460 --> 00:39:40,590
What about me?

557
00:39:41,340 --> 00:39:42,440
You...

558
00:39:43,950 --> 00:39:46,000
were never a part of my life.

559
00:39:47,810 --> 00:39:48,910
Chen Meng Zhen!

560
00:39:55,480 --> 00:39:59,210
Didn't you tell me
to think our relationship through?

561
00:40:00,270 --> 00:40:02,200
That is why I'm here today.

562
00:40:03,700 --> 00:40:05,320
I've thought about it long ago.

563
00:40:07,660 --> 00:40:09,330
You are Xiao Jun's mother.

564
00:40:09,950 --> 00:40:10,930
In your heart,

565
00:40:12,070 --> 00:40:13,610
no one can replace him.

566
00:40:15,680 --> 00:40:18,770
When my father asked me
if I was ready...

567
00:40:19,510 --> 00:40:21,090
to accept him,

568
00:40:21,530 --> 00:40:24,570
the reason I did not answer
wasn't because I was unsure,

569
00:40:24,650 --> 00:40:27,640
but because to me, this wasn't
something I had to think about at all.

570
00:40:29,820 --> 00:40:31,050
I even thought that...

571
00:40:32,260 --> 00:40:34,070
we won't have our own children
in the future.

572
00:40:35,760 --> 00:40:37,110
He alone is enough.

573
00:40:43,770 --> 00:40:45,280
That's what I thought.

574
00:40:45,910 --> 00:40:48,050
But I couldn't bring myself
to tell them.

575
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:50,900
In that situation,

576
00:40:53,900 --> 00:40:55,610
I wouldn't want to tell you either.

577
00:40:56,220 --> 00:40:57,960
I thought maybe I was being hasty.

578
00:40:59,020 --> 00:41:00,480
That you wouldn't believe me.

579
00:41:12,750 --> 00:41:13,850
Why me?

580
00:41:16,080 --> 00:41:17,130
Maybe it's fate.

581
00:41:18,640 --> 00:41:20,150
The whys don't matter.

582
00:41:20,930 --> 00:41:22,500
I just know we get along.

583
00:41:23,110 --> 00:41:25,210
From the moment I met you.

584
00:41:27,020 --> 00:41:28,120
Get along?

585
00:41:28,680 --> 00:41:30,380
So my credentials don't matter.

586
00:41:31,030 --> 00:41:33,610
Even if I'm not the best, right?

587
00:41:33,700 --> 00:41:35,480
-Right.
-But it matters to me.

588
00:41:36,550 --> 00:41:39,410
The man I want to marry
has to see me as the best.

589
00:41:39,500 --> 00:41:42,590
My family and career,
everything I've gone through,

590
00:41:42,680 --> 00:41:44,340
has created the best version of me today.

591
00:41:44,860 --> 00:41:47,580
He would marry me because he knows
he's making the best choice,

592
00:41:47,670 --> 00:41:49,730
not because he's making a huge sacrifice.

593
00:41:49,990 --> 00:41:51,170
I care about that.

594
00:41:52,510 --> 00:41:53,820
I don't see the difference!

595
00:41:53,910 --> 00:41:55,610
It's just semantics!

596
00:41:58,340 --> 00:41:59,245
There is,

597
00:41:59,330 --> 00:42:00,260
Dr. Zhang.

598
00:42:01,190 --> 00:42:03,850
Maybe you're used to having
everything go your way.

599
00:42:04,340 --> 00:42:08,670
You've never seen the other road that
is full of potholes and covered in mud.

600
00:42:09,950 --> 00:42:11,860
Sacrifice is a momentary satisfaction.

601
00:42:13,230 --> 00:42:17,250
It has to be sincere acceptance
for two to...

602
00:42:18,940 --> 00:42:20,320
This is what my late husband said,

603
00:42:21,170 --> 00:42:22,960
when he proposed to me.

604
00:42:24,990 --> 00:42:26,730
I still remember now that he's gone.

605
00:42:28,380 --> 00:42:29,800
He wasn't as polished as you.

606
00:42:30,070 --> 00:42:31,690
He was a brute military man.

607
00:42:33,970 --> 00:42:36,070
I was his biggest pride.

608
00:42:40,250 --> 00:42:41,580
Am I yours?

609
00:42:47,760 --> 00:42:49,780
We are from two different worlds.

610
00:42:50,350 --> 00:42:51,370
The closer we get,

611
00:42:52,060 --> 00:42:53,080
the harder it becomes.

612
00:43:21,170 --> 00:43:23,250
Do you know why we asked you to come?

613
00:43:23,420 --> 00:43:26,333
There was an explosion
at the neighbourhood Xia Chu lives.

614
00:43:26,980 --> 00:43:27,960
Who did it?

615
00:43:30,010 --> 00:43:32,780
According to the news,
it was a delivery guy.

616
00:43:32,940 --> 00:43:34,160
We have tested...

617
00:43:34,590 --> 00:43:37,450
the traces of the explosive
found at the scene.

618
00:43:37,670 --> 00:43:42,030
The deliveryman had used a very
professional variety of the C-4 bomb.

619
00:43:42,270 --> 00:43:43,140
Previously,

620
00:43:43,230 --> 00:43:46,820
the composition bomb that was used
in the Isaia incident,

621
00:43:46,910 --> 00:43:49,170
was very similar
to the one used this time.

622
00:43:49,940 --> 00:43:52,780
Should I say this is T4's signature?

623
00:43:54,030 --> 00:43:56,930
When Old Master's goods
were confiscated at the border,

624
00:43:57,220 --> 00:43:58,480
he mentioned this to me.

625
00:43:59,180 --> 00:44:01,360
That he'd get revenge in Ningjiang.

626
00:44:01,600 --> 00:44:02,990
Why didn't you say anything?

627
00:44:03,075 --> 00:44:05,020
-I thought he wouldn't dare.
-You thought?

628
00:44:05,110 --> 00:44:06,220
Because of your assumption,

629
00:44:06,310 --> 00:44:08,500
Officer Rao and Officer Li
are hospitalized.

630
00:44:08,590 --> 00:44:10,320
My mother is in his hands.

631
00:44:10,740 --> 00:44:12,080
Her life is at stake.

632
00:44:22,350 --> 00:44:25,050
How did he get in touch
with the deliveryman?

633
00:44:25,360 --> 00:44:26,940
City of Desire.

634
00:44:28,070 --> 00:44:29,210
Scary Pirate.

635
00:44:29,590 --> 00:44:31,210
Scary Pirate?

636
00:44:31,870 --> 00:44:32,970
That's Old Master?

637
00:44:34,870 --> 00:44:36,730
Scary Pirate is just an ID.

638
00:44:37,040 --> 00:44:37,990
Isn't it?

639
00:44:38,380 --> 00:44:39,690
If Old Master wants it,

640
00:44:40,100 --> 00:44:43,260
anyone can be the person using the ID.

641
00:44:48,020 --> 00:44:50,000
Ask him what Old Master's goal is.

642
00:44:51,320 --> 00:44:54,290
Why did Old Master do this?

643
00:44:56,230 --> 00:44:57,680
Maybe it's for revenge.

644
00:44:58,370 --> 00:44:59,590
Listen carefully.

645
00:45:00,330 --> 00:45:02,150
If you wish to save your mother,

646
00:45:03,150 --> 00:45:04,730
you better buckle up.

647
00:45:05,050 --> 00:45:06,890
We expect your full cooperation
in the investigation,

648
00:45:07,510 --> 00:45:08,930
and subsequent operation.

649
00:45:28,890 --> 00:45:30,840
Thank you for watching my stream.

650
00:45:30,930 --> 00:45:33,360
If you enjoyed it,
tomorrow at 7:30 p.m.,

651
00:45:33,450 --> 00:45:35,590
I'll be here waiting for you all
at Room 2924.

652
00:45:35,930 --> 00:45:37,150
Love you!

653
00:45:49,960 --> 00:45:52,030
(Zhuo Ran)

654
00:46:01,710 --> 00:46:02,590
Hello.

655
00:46:03,870 --> 00:46:05,100
Nice song.

656
00:46:05,190 --> 00:46:06,290
2924.

657
00:46:06,600 --> 00:46:07,900
You watched my live stream?

658
00:46:08,270 --> 00:46:09,930
It was more interesting than I thought.

659
00:46:10,910 --> 00:46:12,380
Thanks for the compliment.

660
00:46:12,470 --> 00:46:14,850
You have no idea
the amount of preparation I have to do,

661
00:46:14,950 --> 00:46:16,570
for the 2-hour stream every night.

662
00:46:16,980 --> 00:46:19,010
What about your work?

663
00:46:20,910 --> 00:46:22,570
I still do it. This is extra income.

664
00:46:22,750 --> 00:46:24,080
It doesn't affect my main job.

665
00:46:24,280 --> 00:46:26,330
Later, I still have to update my website.

666
00:46:26,640 --> 00:46:27,670
So hardworking.

667
00:46:28,070 --> 00:46:29,010
Aren't you tired?

668
00:46:29,260 --> 00:46:30,095
I am.

669
00:46:30,180 --> 00:46:31,250
How could I not be tired?

670
00:46:32,120 --> 00:46:33,340
But no matter how tired,

671
00:46:33,870 --> 00:46:36,080
I just have to sit by the full-height
window of my house,

672
00:46:36,850 --> 00:46:38,540
and I'll feel like my energy...

673
00:46:39,210 --> 00:46:42,200
has been recharged.

674
00:46:44,040 --> 00:46:44,980
Zhuo Ran.

675
00:46:45,080 --> 00:46:48,070
Back then, why did you leave
without saying goodbye?

676
00:46:48,890 --> 00:46:50,280
Did Xia Chu ask you to ask me?

677
00:46:50,370 --> 00:46:51,250
No.

678
00:46:51,830 --> 00:46:53,290
I'm the one who wants to know.

679
00:46:54,010 --> 00:46:55,700
Is it because of your father?

680
00:46:56,720 --> 00:46:58,380
Why did you suddenly bring him up?
